  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improving Coordination and Response to Displacement Crises</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through this project, IOM&#x2019;s Department of Operations and Emergencies (DOE) actively seeks to improve coordination of, and responses to, displacement crises that lead to long term impacts and, as such, the department is taking active steps to integrate programming at its headquarters and aims to increase its capacity to support field operations and coordination in doing the same. This will be backed up by a global network of regional thematic specialists with a focus on emergency and postcrisis operations.</narrative>
  </description>
